SUMMARY:Seniors Active Living Fair 2026
DESCRIPTION:On March 11th\, 10:00 AM to 02:00 PM\, University Settlement is hosting the Seniors Active Living Fair\, a free community event designed to support healthy\, active\, and independent living for older adults. \nThe event is open to everyone – whether you are a senior\, caregiver\, or family member of a senior resident\, you are invited to join us this March for a day of connection\, learning\, and fun!  \nWe have programs and activities planned for you and your family. Join us at this year’s Seniors Fair!  \nVisit our website for more information: Seniors Active Living Fair \nWhat to Expect \n\nInformation booths from health\, wellness\, and community organizations\nProgram demonstrations and on-site sign-ups\nInteractive sessions including crochet\, simple dance workshops\, and acrylic painting\nPresentations on chronic disease prevention and senior services\nLight lunch snacks and refreshments
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/seniors-active-living-fair-2026/
LOCATION:23 Grange Road\, 23 Grange Rd\, Toronto\, ON M5T 1C3\, Canada\, Old Toronto\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M5T 1C3
CATEGORIES:Community Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/seniors-active-living-fair-2026.png
END:VEVENT
