UID:10239011-1773257400-1773264600@nowtoronto.com
SUMMARY:The Dancing Djinn CABARET
DESCRIPTION:An Acclaimed Immersive Cabaret Returns to Toronto’s Legendary Lula Lounge \nFollowing sold-out performances and standing ovations across Canada\, The Dancing Djinn Cabaret returns to Toronto for a special show at the legendary Lula Lounge. \nThe Dancing Djinn Cabaret is an immersive theatrical and musical experience combining live singing\, original music\, bellydance\, drag\, shadowplay\, and cabaret storytelling. The show is created and performed by Nikotine\, host and Arabesque vocalist\, and Samara\, bellydancing icon\, both Lebanese immigrants immersed in drag\, theatre\, and performance entertainment. \nNikotine has been traveling through the desert for so long that she has forgotten where she comes from or where she was going. All she has is a magic lamp that whispers to her in the night. Rumor has it that a dangerous djinn lives inside: the spirit of Samara\, ancient Queen of Queerabia. Inspired by ancient Andalusian queer Arabic poetry and Sufi mysticism\, the show is rooted in storytelling\, humor\, and shadowplay. \nBilingual English-Arabic rock\, piano ballads\, and jazz cabaret are performed entirely live\, with no lip-syncing\, within a rich Arabesque visual world. Hand-beaded costumes complement the historic elegance of Arabian bellydance\, storyline and history. The show is funny\, alive\, exciting and deeply moving. \nPresented in an intimate cabaret format\, the show unfolds in close proximity to the audience. Performers move between stage and room\, following a theatrical through-line that transforms the evening into a shared experience. Audiences often describe the show as joyful\, moving\, and unexpectedly transformative. \nAudience praise includes: \n“The best show I’ve ever seen at the Lula Lounge.” – Alex S. \n“I didn’t know what to expect\, but I was really blown away. I left transformed\, like fully transformed. It felt like a ritual.” – Najma W. \nBlending cabaret\, musical theatre\, and performance art\, The Dancing Djinn Cabaret offers a rare live experience that celebrates storytelling\, cultural exchange\, and the razzledazzle of performance.
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/the-dancing-djinn-cabaret/
LOCATION:Lula Lounge\, 1585 Dundas St W\, Toronto\, M6K 1T9
CATEGORIES:2SLGBTQ+,Dance,Live Music,Nightlife,Performing Arts,Theatre & Opera
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/the-dancing-djinn-cabaret.png
END:VEVENT
