SUMMARY:Replay Storytelling: When We Were Kids
DESCRIPTION:Do you remember your 10th birthday? I’m pretty sure we will remember ours\,  because this March\, Replay Storytelling turns 10 years-old! \nReplay Storytelling presents When We Were Kids\, true stories of the children we used to be! \n🎟️ Tickets are $20 in advance\, or $25 at the door. 💻 This show will be live-streamed\, live-stream tickets are $20. \nGet your tickets now: https://www.replaystorytelling.com/tickets/ \nCome celebrate our 10th anniversary with true tales from the innocence\, wonder\, and adventures that shaped our lives. \n🖍️ Replay Storytelling presents When We Were Kids📍 Burdock Music Hall | 1184 Bloor Street West📅 Wednesday\, March 11th\, 2026🕢 Doors 7pm | Show at 7:30pm \nLearn more about Replay Storytelling at www.replaystorytelling.com
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/replay-storytelling-when-we-were-kids/
LOCATION:Burdock Brewery & Music Hall\, 1184 Bloor St W\, Toronto\, ON M6H 1N2\, Canada\, Old Toronto\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M6H 1N2
CATEGORIES:Literature & Spoken Word,Performing Arts,Talks & Panels
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/replay-storytelling-when-we-were-kids.png
END:VEVENT
