SUMMARY:Circle Mirror Transformation
DESCRIPTION:Circle Mirror transformation is a play. Set over a six-week-long community-centre drama class & how it transforms four lost humans and their teacher. The story is beautifully crafted diorama of tiny wars and quite heartbreaks\, tinged with humour and sadness\, from Pulitzer-Prize-winning playwright Annie Baker.
